public class Axis2SynapseEnvironmentFinder
extends java.lang.Object
implements Constants

The SynapseEnvironment needs to be set up and then is used by the SynapseMessageReceiver to inject messages. This class is used by the SynapseMessageReceiver to find the environment. The env is stored in a Parameter to the Axis2 config
